{"tid":1379080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［急］義勇軍進行曲！示威期間振奮人心！","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T18:15:10.000Z","uid":291909,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"491edf405f07a442e0665b5d49a1a3a42029fac9","tid":1379080,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:34:32.000Z","msg":"我地嘅偉大祖國，國歌都有教<br />\n<br />\n比人蝦嘅晚時候，係要反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度正正反映我哋需要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">民主</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">起來，不願做奴隸的人們</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">中華民族</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到了最危險的時候。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每個人被迫著發出最後的吼聲. 起來! 起來! 起來！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我們萬眾一心，冒着敵人的炮火前進！<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火！前進！前進！前進進！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進攻時大家一齊唱國歌！如果<br />\n<br />\n最後一句：連國歌都支持我地，為我地發聲！<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好擅自改國歌歌詞，犯罪嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔知「中華民族轉左做<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港民主</span>」會點呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我乜都唔知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反抗吧！革命軍！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a0016d2478f86ec532f703646d3501e587e623c9","tid":1379080,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco